node.text: “My work centers Black joy, community, and love. I hope that it makes others feel seen, held, and welcome in all their complexities,” says Chiomma Hall of @chiommani. Watch to learn more about how her beautiful prints draw from the intersections of her identity to portray BIPOC and LGBTQIA+ communities reveling in rest, choosing self-care, and communing with loved ones. Then visit her Etsy shop to admire her art: etsy.me/chiommani
